snippet.title: Let's Sing ABBA | Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Let's Sing ABBA is out today!

https://bit.ly/LSABBAcg

Become a Dancing Queen or a Super Trouper in the Summer Night City or while celebrating a Happy New Year. 

You can either play alone or grab some friends to start your karaoke party. When All Is Said And Done we’d like to Thank You For The Music and hope you enjoy the experience that is Let’s Sing Presents ABBA.

#LetsSingABBA #ABBA #Karaoke
